welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Saint-Brice-sous-Foret, a charming city known for its picturesque landscapes and rich history. We invite you to immerse yourself in our culture and explore all that our beautiful city has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Terminal 2
terminals.description: A smaller terminal at Le Bourget Airport, mainly used for private and chartered flights.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.
